Root .gitignore for user-agent-honeypot mono‑repo

-------------------------------------------------

▸ Keep the repo portable between macOS host, Windows VM, Docker builds,

WebStorm/VS Code, and Visual Studio.

--- IDE / Editor junk -------------------------------------------------------

.idea/
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json   # keep extension recommendations
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

--- OS / swap / temp --------------------------------------------------------

*.sw?
*.swo
*.swn

--- Node / JavaScript -------------------------------------------------------

node_modules/
dist/
build/
coverage/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

--- Environment & secrets ---------------------------------------------------

.env*

e.g. .env, .env.local, .env.production

--- Databases / runtime artefacts ------------------------------------------

*.db
.sqlite
logs/
*.log
*.pid

--- Docker artefacts --------------------------------------------------------

*.tar
.docker/
docker-compose.override.yml

--- Visual Studio (Windows VM) ---------------------------------------------

*.sln
*.suo
.ntvs
*.njsproj

--- Packet captures ---------------------------------------------------------

*.pcap
*.pcapng

--- Misc --------------------------------------------------------------------

*.bak
*~

